          "paperId": "3667238486024192",
          "source": "专题二  简单直流电路",
          "year": 2025,
          "difficulty": 0.65,
          "stem": "<div class=\"qml-stem\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">两个电阻</span><math latex=\"$R_{1}$\"><mrow><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><math latex=\"$R_{2}$\"><mrow><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，已知</span><math latex=\"$R_{1}\\colon R_{2}=1\\colon 2$\"><mrow><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。若它们在电路中并联，则两电阻上的电压比</span><math latex=\"$U_{1}\\colon U_{2}=$\"><mrow><msub><mi>U</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi>U</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo></mrow></math><span class=\"qml-bk\" index=\"1\" size=\"4\" type=\"underline\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\" >　　　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；两电阻上的电流比</span><math latex=\"$I_{1}\\colon I_{2}=$\"><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi>I</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo></mrow></math><span class=\"qml-bk\" index=\"2\" size=\"4\" type=\"underline\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\" >　　　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；它们消耗的功率比</span><math latex=\"$P_{1}\\colon P_{2}=$\"><mrow><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo></mrow></math><span class=\"qml-bk\" index=\"3\" size=\"4\" type=\"underline\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\" >　　　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></p></div>",
          "answer": "<div class=\"qml-answer\"><span class=\"qml-an-sq\">① <span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">∶</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">1</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;② <span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">∶</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">1</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;③ <span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">∶</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">1</span></span></span></div>",
          "explanation": "<div class=\"qml-explanation\"><div class=\"qml-seg\" seg-name=\"详解\">【详解】<p style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">并联电路中电压相等。</span></p><p style=\"\"><math latex=\"$I=\\frac{U}{R}\\newline I_{1}\\colon I_{2}=\\frac{U}{R_{1}}\\colon \\frac{U}{R_{2}}=\\frac{R_{2}}{R_{1}}=2\\colon 1$\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>U</mi><mi>R</mi></mfrac><mspace linebreak=\"newline\"></mspace><msub><mi>I</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi>I</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>U</mi><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>:</mo><mfrac><mi>U</mi><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>1</mn></math></p><p style=\"\"><math latex=\"$P=\\frac{U^{2}}{R}\\newline P_{1}\\colon P_{2}=\\frac{U^{2}}{R_{1}}\\colon \\frac{U^{2}}{R_{2}}=\\frac{R_{2}}{R_{1}}=2\\colon 1$\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>U</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>R</mi></mfrac><mspace linebreak=\"newline\"></mspace><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>U</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>:</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>U</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>1</mn></math></p></div></div>",
